issue.description:
The order of the attributes in Group_relationship  is incorrect.

ENTITY Group_relationship;
  relation_type : STRING;
  relating_group : Group;
  related_group : Group;
  description : OPTIONAL STRING;
END_ENTITY;

It should be:

ENTITY Group_relationship;
  description : OPTIONAL STRING;
  relation_type : STRING;
  relating_group : Group;
  related_group : Group;
END_ENTITY;
